products.name: Chums Original
products.description: The easily adjustable Chums Original retainer  is the product that put us on the map. Millions agree: it is ideal for all forms of action, be it on water, land, snow, or in the air. The original cotton eyeglass retainer has it all: quality, comfort, and the ability to fit most standard frames.
products.details:
• Fits standard-sized frames
  • Bead adjusts for superb fit
  • Hand wash with mild soap. Rinse thoroughly. Stretch to original length.
  • Made in the USA
  • Customization available
  • Length: 14.5"
  • Usable length: 25"
  • Weight without packaging: 0.4 oz.
